{"tid":1524760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地邏輯錯撚哂!要美國幫手vs be water只能任擇其一!","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T20:57:30.000Z","uid":211469,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6672df4779cd1594742dc2813df184b2c41e9398","tid":1524760,"uid":211469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"侵侵已經講明會<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">觀察呢兩三日嘅形勢發展</span></span></strong></strong>，決定係唔係出手相助<br />\n所以，如果我地confirm想美國幫手，就要響呢兩三日觀察期內令局勢升級，俾機會侵侵出手！<br />\n但另一方面我地又成日叫「be water」、「留力」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞到唔上唔落咁，美國又點有藉口出到手呀？？？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想推人送頭，但大家真係要搞清楚，究竟係想要：<br />\n(A)be water，但係只能靠自己；定係<br />\n(B)靠美國，但要令局勢升級（要再玩大Ｄ）？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n兩個option只可揀一個，冇得兩全其美！<br />\n<br />\n要緊記，好多革命真係要靠外國幫手，毛澤東、孫中山...等等！尤其是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">我地面對嘅唔單止係林鄭,而係<span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span>!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我真心覺得，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">單靠我地自己，一撚定打&mdash;唔&mdash;贏！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候諗下點樣俾機會美國出手喇！唔好再諗乜９持久戰、be water喇！盡快引美國出手啦！我地頂唔到幾耐架啦！個人愚見，要再玩大D!"},{"pid":"b42fc14da61b76f15362e2c8ac917cfe9a239ea3","tid":1524760,"uid":211469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"UP!"},{"pid":"117fd03a6095aafdf3c1c1057dc615ab0f46651d","tid":1524760,"uid":211469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"up!!"},{"pid":"2dc0bc1ebdd9019be3f5cd5119def3487cc694fa","tid":1524760,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:57:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際路線】全世界印依款標語</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTpDjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTpDjV.png&h=ada7f3ab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}